    "date": "2025-08-08T16:59:02Z",
    "text": "North Platte Canteen Congressional Gold Medal Act\n\nThis bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to recognize the individuals and communities that provided financial and other support for the North Platte Canteen in North Platte, Nebraska, during World War II."
